text: RT @drunk: If you love someone, set them free. If they don't come back, text them when you're drunk

First sentence said to me as I walk on into my shift, “You look tired!”
Ok, well eff me then...going to be a long day.
How do girls have a full face of makeup on at 4:00 am? I can’t even put my shoes on the corect foot this early.
RT @wordstionary: You'll be surprised to know how far you can go from the point where you thought it was the end.
Is an “IOU” acceptable as a wedding gift? Asking for a friend...
